{"tid":672760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話你知, 好多自豪有份交稅既港豬仲係唔知支那狗未夠7年都可以咬老綜","createTime":"2018-05-21T09:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T05:41:40.000Z","uid":111253,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1bea8e2824f13c1e4cc620b01ece906dd81f93d1","tid":672760,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幾時開始呢? <br />\n答案係 2013年<br />\n唔遠架！ 5年前架咋！<br />\n<br />\n好, 俾張圖你睇下</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/felaile_y7nJo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffelaile_y7nJo_1200x0.png&h=a74d2538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014~2017年期, <br />\n每個年度食你起碼<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5億以上</span></span></strong>, <br />\n你班離地中產睇下自己交稅養緊咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再睇下D膠官點回應&darr;<br />\n<br />\n有市民質疑關愛基金幫助新來港人士，惟未有「到位」幫助港人，批評政府歧視港人。<br />\n勞福局局長羅致光回應指，現時大部分新移民是高學歷或專業人士；<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">申請綜援的新來港人士  與  <br />\n整體港人的申請人數  比例相若</span></span></strong>，<br />\n重申政府沒偏重新來港人士，目前關愛基金亦沒有項目來幫助新移民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下幾撚戇鳩!? 咁都講得出!?   <br />\n我當你整體港人有600萬人口, 6萬人咬老綜;<br />\n整體支那狗有100萬人口, 5萬人咬老綜, <br />\n你話「相若」丫嘛,<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6萬/600萬  VS  5萬/100萬</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n傻閪都知幾撚有問題啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe0796f87a0f2dc9af294973f38665c7ca79a92","tid":672760,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623ef754ae446ca6c9f04e9eb73c19e15b46a71c","tid":672760,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2fbdb49488f1b6a6987ffa0d634ffd75e567d4","tid":672760,"uid":17765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"班閪人自己層樓/股票升就收埋把閪口㗎啦"},{"pid":"eff2ac1e890c636d397f0848e866b753c27e7e0f","tid":672760,"uid":105538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be973c9c112fad01be34239b067c89a1dc58e81f","tid":672760,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:32:07.0